text: Nuwan Liyanapathirana (born 22 May 1987) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Sri Lanka Army Sports Club in the 2008–09 Premier Trophy on 16 January 2009. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Sri Lanka Army Sports Club cricketers Category:People from Central Province, Sri Lanka
